rows.label: tlk42350122_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Do you know Iraada Village? It's a
small village on the edge of Gula.

rows.label: tlk42350122_02_msg0002
rows.name:
That village is great. The water is
clear and the villagers are kind.

rows.label: tlk42350122_02_msg0003
rows.name:
A boy named Lilio in particular
was very fond of us.

rows.label: tlk42350122_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I haven't been to Iraada
Village recently, but I
wonder if Lilio is doing well.
